long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Jalios JReading Web Extension is an excellent tool that can help JPlatform users to read a web page later by adding this page in his reading list with a simple click.

Note : To use Jalios JReading Web Extension, you should configure your JPlatform URL.
